OL,3,C'From having everything to nothing' -
OL,4,CAsylum seekers shed light with
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FHelen Carnell went along to see the
OL,8,Fexhibition before it opened.
OL,10,FAn exhibition which seeks to shed
OL,11,Flight on the reality of the UK's
OL,12,Fasylum system has opened at the Baltic
OL,13,FCentre in Gateshead.
OL,15,FThe exhibition has been curated by
OL,16,Frefugees and asylum seekers who have
OL,17,Ffaced being part of the system.
