OL,3,C'From having everything to nothing' -
OL,4,CAsylum seekers shed light with
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FPhotographs, and the stories that
OL,8,Faccompany them, are on display as part
OL,9,Fof We All Came Here From Somewhere
OL,10,Fexhibition, open from 23 November to 9
OL,11,FFebruary, which explores how the North
OL,12,FEast can welcome people seeking
OL,13,Fsanctuary in the region.
OL,15,FFor some of those involved in the
OL,16,Fexhibition, the summer riots raised
OL,17,Fquestions about why people become
OL,18,Fhostile towards those from other
OL,19,Fplaces.
