OL,3,C'From having everything to nothing' -
OL,4,CAsylum seekers shed light with
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FOne of the refugee artists Grace
OL,8,FMbuende, from Namibia, told ITV Tyne
OL,9,FTees: "It was very hard to see how
OL,10,Fhostile some people can be.
OL,12,F"People usually reject what they do
OL,13,Fnot know.
OL,15,F"Awareness is at the forefront of it
OL,16,Fall."
OL,18,FArtist Sadia Sikandar, who was born
OL,19,Fand raised in Pakistan, is an award-
OL,20,Fwinning photographer, teacher and
OL,21,Fcampaigner.
