OL,3,C'From having everything to nothing' -
OL,4,CAsylum seekers shed light with
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FShe was forced to seek asylum in the
OL,8,FUK in 2018 where she faced a six-year
OL,9,Fbattle for refugee status during which
OL,10,Ftime she spent time homeless and, like
OL,11,Fall people claiming asylum, was banned
OL,12,Ffrom working.
OL,14,FSadia said: "In my home country I had
OL,15,Fa job, a car and a home, but I lacked
OL,16,Ffreedom and peace of mind.
OL,18,F"My life was in danger, which is
OL,19,Fsomething people need to understand.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
