OL,3,C'From having everything to nothing' -
OL,4,CAsylum seekers shed light with
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,F"Asylum seekers are often viewed as
OL,8,Fthough we come from impoverished or
OL,9,Fjobless backgrounds, but in reality, I
OL,10,Fhad a very good status in Pakistan.
OL,12,F"I came here because my life was at
OL,13,Frisk.
OL,15,F"For those of us who seek asylum, it
OL,16,Foften means going from having
OL,17,Feverything to having nothing.
OL,19,F"This experience strips away our
OL,20,Fdignity, honour and self-respect."
