OL,3,C'From having everything to nothing' -
OL,4,CAsylum seekers shed light with
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FIn 2022 the Baltic was awarded Gallery
OL,8,Fof Sanctuary status as part of a
OL,9,Fmovement started in Sheffield 19 years
OL,10,Fago by the charity City of Sanctuary.
OL,12,FAs part of that status they hold
OL,13,Flanguage cafes where people can meet
OL,14,Fnew people and informally practise
OL,15,Ftheir English.
